author: Solid jj
description:
Superman meets with Martian Manhunter and his parents, the Kents, as they celebrate Christmas together under one roof. However, the question of Santa Clause causes division in the household as Superman believes in the big man. This is a real fact from the Justice League cartoon, he believes. As he should.
